OL,4,G0135FHetty Wainthropp Investigates
OL,5,     GGillian Snape's family are
OL,6,     Gconvinced that Lester Rose wants
OL,7,     Gto marry her only for her money.
OL,8,     GHetty has just one week to
OL,9,     Ginvestigate whether his love for
OL,10,     GGillian is genuine.
OL,11,G0225FThe Good Old Days
OL,12,     GLeonard Sachs presents the silver
OL,13,     Gjubilee edition of the old-time
OL,14,     Gmusic hall programme, first
OL,15,     Gbroadcast on 10 January 1978.
OL,16,     GWith Ken Dodd and Jan Hunt.
OL,17,G0315FSquirrel on My Shoulder -
OL,18,     FWildlife on One
